			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Identified is currently seeking interns to work with the sales and marketing teams. The position will allow students to be at the forefront of the constantly changing landscape of social media and will provide the thrill of working at a fast-growing and dynamic startup. Interns will work closely with our entire team and play a critical role in shaping Identified&rsquo;s future growth. Working for Identified will lead interns to learn from our investors, including venture capitalists Eric Schmidt, the CEO of Google, and Bill Draper, the proclaimed &#39;godfather of Silicon Valley&rsquo;s oldest VC dynasty.&rsquo; Ideal candidates are those with a strong work ethic, excellent communication skills and a technological mindset keen on searching for innovative internet solutions. If you have the perspective and appetite to be a part of the &#39;The Wild Wild West&#39; of social media, apply now on Identified.com.</p>
<p>
	<br />
	Company Overview<br />
	Identified is a fast-growing San Francisco-based startup that is developing a powerful new way for companies and potential hires to connect by leveraging the Facebook social graph. Identified&rsquo;s disruptive technology overlays the social graph on top of the traditional career center and headhunting processes to enable companies and applicants to connect directly with the power of instant referrals, analytics &amp; information and dynamic Q&amp;A.<br />
	Identified launched at the MBA program at Stanford University 10 months ago and gained significant traction. Within 2 weeks the site had nearly 80% of the student population enrolled and students were placed in jobs and internships within days of the launch. In fact, there were 2x more students on Identified than were using the career center! Since then, Identified has grown very quickly at elite universities across the country and now has over 12,000 students from Harvard, Princeton, Yale, UPenn, Brown, UVA, Columbia, Berkeley and a number of other top schools. Furthermore, nearly 1,100 companies have signed up to use Identified and the company has placed candidates in a significant number of jobs across a variety of industries and companies.<br />
	Social media is changing the way people think about the future of the internet. And further, online social communities are quickly becoming the backbone of the internet&rsquo;s growth and evolution. Identified is leading the charge in harnessing the power of social to recreate the professional network for the future. Building on existing social networks like Linkedln and especially Facebook, Identified is on the cutting edge of exploiting the benefits social media while protecting the reputation of a person&rsquo;s professional online identity.<br />
	Identified has raised $5.5M from an amazing set of investors that includes Bill Draper, Eric Schmidt, John Glynn, and a number of top Silicon Valley Angel investors. We&rsquo;ve grown to 18 employees and created an incredibly young, dynamic and exciting work environment where the ambitions are sky-high.<br />
	Send resumes directly to Stuart Rogers at stuart@identified.com.</p>
